WEBVTT

2
00:00:03.091 --> 00:00:07.073
Nau mai ki tēnei whakaaturanga a ipurangi o te tēpu,

3
00:00:07.073 --> 00:00:11.002
kei te take kōrero tātou mō Whakaata Māori.

4
00:00:11.002 --> 00:00:16.024
Kei te tutukia rānei te hiahia kia pāho nuitia tō tātou reo rangatira,

5
00:00:16.024 --> 00:00:18.081
kei te pēhea kē rānei?

6
00:00:18.081 --> 00:00:22.058
Kei konei ngā kaikōrero he kaipāpāho katoa.

7
00:00:22.058 --> 00:00:27.051
Te Waihoroi Shortland, Stacey Morrison, Eruera Morgan, tēnā koutou,

8
00:00:27.051 --> 00:00:29.046
anei te pātai, Eruera,

9
00:00:29.046 --> 00:00:35.014
mā te ao pāpāho ka ora te reo Māori, pīki tika, pīki teka rānei.

10
00:00:35.014 --> 00:00:39.063
Ehara mā te pouaka whakaata Māori anake e ora ai tō tātou reo.

11
00:00:39.063 --> 00:00:40.066
Nā reira pīki teka

12
00:00:40.066 --> 00:00:46.084
nā te mea kei te kaha whakapono tātou mā te ao pāpāho ka ora te reo Māori.

13
00:00:46.084 --> 00:00:50.047
roa e kōrerohia ana. He aha ō whakaaro,

14
00:00:50.047 --> 00:00:54.029
e ora ana te reo mā te pouaka whakaata Māori.

15
00:00:54.029 --> 00:00:55.089
Me pērā taku whakautu.

16
00:00:55.089 --> 00:01:00.055
Engari kaua mā te...Pouaka Whakaata anake.

17
00:01:00.055 --> 00:01:07.082
Tekau tau te pakeke, station, 10 tau te pakeke o te teihana kei te whakatinanahia te tūmanako.

18
00:01:07.082 --> 00:01:16.079
En gari, kua eke taumata i ētahi wā, engari me whai tonu i te pae tawhiti, koinā tāku.

19
00:01:16.079 --> 00:01:18.061
Me whiu anō au tēnā pātai.

20
00:01:18.061 --> 00:01:24.017
Mā te ao pāpāho tō tātou reo Māori e ora ai

21
00:01:24.017 --> 00:01:29.002
e kore māna e ora ai.

22
00:01:29.002 --> 00:01:35.083
Māna e noho e kitea whānui ai, e rongohia whānui ai,

23
00:01:35.083 --> 00:01:39.044
mā te iwi anake te reo ka ora.

24
00:01:39.044 --> 00:01:44.040
Kāhore mā... mā ngā taputapu nei kia...

25
00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:47.093
kia manawanui te iwi ki tana reo,

26
00:01:47.093 --> 00:01:57.009
ko te mahi a tēnei Hōngere e whaka piki i taua manawanui.

27
00:01:57.009 --> 00:01:59.032
Kāhore i tua atu i tērā

28
00:01:59.032 --> 00:02:04.075
kei te eke te mahi a te whakaata Māori  i runga i tēnā whakaaro.

29
00:02:04.075 --> 00:02:07.087
Kei te ahu atu ia i runga i te huarahi tika.

30
00:02:07.087 --> 00:02:10.085
Tēnā koe kōrua, koutou māmā.

31
00:02:10.085 --> 00:02:17.031
E hoa mā, hei whakamākūkū i te korokoro te tikanga o tēnei whakaaturanga poto, Whakaata

32
00:02:17.031 --> 00:02:34.085
tēnā kia rangona te roanga atu o ngā kōrero huri mai ki a tēpu haurua o te iwa pō Wenerei Māori kia mau ō karu.
